To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private AwesomeOscillator _ao;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_ao = AO(symbol, slowPeriod, fastPeriod, type);

// In OnData()
if (_ao.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "slowao", _ao.SlowAo.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "fastao", _ao.FastAo.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "awesomeoscillator", _ao.Current.Value);
}
